  "version": "0.1.2-beta.6",
  "notes": "✨ 新功能 / New Features\r\n\r\n  终端填充配置 / Terminal Padding Configuration\r\n  - 新增终端内边距配置选项，可在设置中自定义上下左右边距\r\n  - Added terminal padding configuration options, allowing customization of top, bottom, left, and right padding in settings\r\n\r\n  自动更新增强 / Auto-Update Enhancements\r\n  - 实现完整的更新下载和安装流程\r\n  - 新增更新日志显示组件，支持 Markdown 格式和 emoji 渲染\r\n  - 添加最后检查更新的时间戳记录\r\n  - Implemented complete update download and installation flow\r\n  - Added release notes display component with Markdown support and emoji handling\r\n  - Added last update check timestamp tracking\r\n\r\n  🐛 问题修复 / Bug Fixes\r\n\r\n  SFTP 文件管理 / SFTP File Management\r\n  - 修复 SFTP 删除操作时的 UI 状态管理问题\r\n  - Fixed UI state management issues during SFTP deletion operations\r\n\r\n  标签页管理 / Tab Management\r\n  - 为传输任务添加 tabId 标识\r\n  - 关闭带有活跃传输的标签页时显示确认对话框\r\n  - Added tabId to transfer tasks\r\n  - Added confirmation dialogs when closing tabs with active transfers\r\n\r\n  更新检查 / Update Check\r\n  - 修复更新检查时间戳的记录逻辑\r\n  - Fixed update check timestamp recording logic\r\n\r\n  ♻️ 代码重构 / Refactoring\r\n\r\n  终端状态管理 / Terminal State Management\r\n  - 改进终端状态管理、对话框处理和窗口控制\r\n  - 提升稳定性和错误处理能力\r\n  - 提取 useTabContextMenu 和 useWindowControls 自定义 hooks\r\n  - Improved terminal state management, dialog handling, and window controls\r\n  - Enhanced stability and error handling\r\n  - Extracted useTabContextMenu and useWindowControls custom hooks\n",
